1
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:20,390
♪Suddenly, you showed up♪

2
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:28,750
♪Who stole away those years♪

3
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:37,320
♪Oh, night and day♪

4
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:45,540
♪Oh, it's been a long time♪

5
00:00:45,930 --> 00:00:50,050
♪Pass through the bustling world
in the daytime♪

6
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,880
♪Circumvent love at night♪

7
00:00:54,010 --> 00:00:57,760
♪Day after day, year after year♪

8
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,040
♪I wake up and close my eyes
before it gets dark♪

9
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:06,140
♪But when the day breaks into the night♪

10
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:10,220
♪It makes me believe
that there's still love♪

11
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:14,050
♪If you want it, if I want it♪

12
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:20,800
♪It's a vow of night and day♪

13
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:32,890
♪It's a vow of day and night♪

14
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:37,200
[Blooming]

15
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,920
[Episode 12]

16
00:01:40,550 --> 00:01:41,190
Then,

17
00:01:41,950 --> 00:01:44,160
have you ever been jealous
because of Qiu Yuebai?

18
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,720
I don't think so.

19
00:01:50,830 --> 00:01:52,830
It's OK. We have another way.

20
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,440
The last one will definitely work.

21
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:58,160
When you fall for someone, you will...

22
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:00,510
You will

23
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:04,950
think about whether he eats well

24
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:06,230
and is warm enough every day.

25
00:02:08,190 --> 00:02:08,800
I see.

26
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:13,000
If he gets hurt,

27
00:02:13,470 --> 00:02:14,630
but I don't feel sorry,

28
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,670
does that mean I don't like him?

29
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:19,160
Probably.

30
00:02:20,830 --> 00:02:21,240
Well,

31
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:25,110
Xueyi, you find a chance to hurt him.

32
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:28,320
If I don't feel sorry,

33
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:31,270
it'll prove that I don't like him.

34
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:33,720
What if he gets hurt badly?

35
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,670
He won't. He's Mu Bai Zhenren.

36
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,390
Mu Bai Zhenren?

37
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:40,550
Aren't we going to test Qiu Yuebai?

38
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:45,880
Let's experiment with Cui Chen first.

39
00:02:46,390 --> 00:02:47,910
Qiu doesn't have any spiritual power.

40
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,550
What if he gets hurt by mistake?

41
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,080
That's right.

42
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,800
[Qionghua Sect]

43
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,630
Any news of Hu Meng?

44
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,960
I've used 5,000 years of my contacts

45
00:03:07,110 --> 00:03:08,800
to get you a little information.

46
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,320
Thank you.

47
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,160
Have some tea to moisten your throat.

48
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:13,440
- Here.
- OK.

49
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,030
It turns out

50
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,960
the golden fox isn't in Yunlai.

51
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,800
She's practicing somewhere else.

52
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:22,720
Where is she?

53
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:24,630
I'm still looking into it.

54
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,550
But I heard

55
00:03:27,670 --> 00:03:28,550
she had a lover.

56
00:03:31,110 --> 00:03:33,470
Yes. She did say

57
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:34,630
she had a lover.

58
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,190
But it was odd.

59
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:38,110
They were suddenly separated.

60
00:03:38,830 --> 00:03:40,670
Hu Meng disappeared for a while.

61
00:03:40,830 --> 00:03:42,960
Then she showed up in Yunlai Town.

62
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:47,550
Did she steal the lotus seed
because of that relationship?

63
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:51,390
Another poor creature deeply in love.

64
00:03:53,390 --> 00:03:54,110
Who are you talking about?

65
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:55,190
You.

66
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:04,390
Go.

67
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,270
Xueyi.

68
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,670
Hurry up.

69
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:12,910
I'm counting on you.

70
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,190
Come on. Go.

71
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:14,520
I...

72
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,270
Hurry.

73
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,390
Tantan, are you OK?

74
00:05:03,110 --> 00:05:03,950
I'm fine.

75
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,270
Senior Mu Bai.

76
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,710
I was picking coconuts.

77
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,710
I accidentally dropped it.

78
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:21,240
Where's the coconut tree?

79
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,200
Tree...

80
00:05:22,550 --> 00:05:24,110
Where is the tree?

81
00:05:25,710 --> 00:05:26,360
Tree...

82
00:05:27,150 --> 00:05:27,920
It was there just now.

83
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,390
Really?

84
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,240
Why are you here？

85
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,270
Tantan asked me to...

86
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,240
Tantan, wait for me.

87
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:42,110
Tantan.

88
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:44,240
So, did you feel sorry for him?

89
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,150
I don't know.

90
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:52,360
The coconut

91
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,640
swooshed right at me.

92
00:05:53,870 --> 00:05:55,480
I didn't have time to react.

93
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,390
It's OK. We can do it again.

94
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:58,990
No.

95
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:01,360
It must hurt badly if he gets hit.

96
00:06:01,990 --> 00:06:04,200
Then he'll tell on me to Master.

97
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,200
I'll be done for.

98
00:06:05,550 --> 00:06:06,960
We won't hit him.

99
00:06:07,110 --> 00:06:09,150
This time we'll test Qiu Yuebai.

100
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,480
Qiu?

101
00:06:11,590 --> 00:06:11,870
Yeah.

102
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,430
Last time we proved

103
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:16,240
that you didn't have feelings
for other men.

104
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:17,990
This time we're going to
prove your feelings

105
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,830
for your destined love.

106
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:22,080
OK.

107
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,710
Tantan,

108
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,520
you seem a little strange.

109
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:28,990
What's strange about me?

110
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,760
OK, tomorrow we'll find out

111
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,640
if I care about Qiu.

112
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:47,800
Tantan.

113
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:51,110
Can I drop it now? My hands are shaking.

114
00:06:51,150 --> 00:06:52,390
Why hasn't he come out yet?

115
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:55,150
Hold on. Hang in there.

116
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:02,200
Xueyi.

117
00:07:02,590 --> 00:07:02,960
Xueyi.

118
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,150
One.

119
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,080
Two.

120
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:12,710
Three.

121
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,080
Tantan!

122
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:35,240
Are you OK?

123
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:38,920
As a cultivator,

124
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:41,040
you didn't even know
how to use magic arts when you fell.

125
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,760
You had to depend on an ordinary man
to save you.

126
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,480
Unbelievable.

127
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:58,040
Why is he annoyed?

128
00:08:04,550 --> 00:08:05,680
Cui Chen.

129
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:10,590
When I was a tadpole,

130
00:08:10,590 --> 00:08:12,150
I could draw better with my tail.

131
00:08:12,590 --> 00:08:13,240
Let me admire it.

132
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:16,960
I see.

133
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,270
Hu Meng.

134
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,110
Lu Yi.

135
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:24,640
Hu Meng.

136
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:25,990
Lu Yi.

137
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,150
Didn't you see the tail?

138
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,430
Isn't it big and obvious?

139
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:29,960
Doesn't it look like her?

140
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:33,440
Forget it.

141
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:33,920
I'll draw again.

142
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:35,560
Let me admire it.

143
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:40,440
Annoyed and upset.
Restless and whimsical.

144
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:41,040
I'm not.

145
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:45,000
I'm putting your painting back.

146
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,280
[It feels both joy and fear.]

147
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:52,510
It feels both joy

148
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:56,240
and fear.

149
00:08:58,800 --> 00:08:59,710
I found it on your desk.

150
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,480
Your destined love is Zhao Tantan.

151
00:09:05,630 --> 00:09:06,510
But

152
00:09:07,190 --> 00:09:08,070
the process and outcome

153
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,830
may not be as smooth

154
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:10,510
as other destined couples.

155
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,120
You may even

156
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,880
bring each other bad things.

157
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,070
Is this the reason?

158
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:19,630
I've heard
about the curse on your forehead

159
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,150
over the past 100 years.

160
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,320
But don't worry, Mr. Cui.

161
00:09:23,590 --> 00:09:24,560
Your feelings for each other

162
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:25,680
are not determinant.

163
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:27,150
If you make great efforts,

164
00:09:27,510 --> 00:09:28,920
you can change your destiny.

165
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,040
Change destiny?

166
00:09:32,590 --> 00:09:34,560
The Xilan Flower Curse
may fall at any moment.

167
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:36,070
How can I be with her?

168
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:43,950
I'd say you young people

169
00:09:43,950 --> 00:09:45,710
tend to complicate matters,

170
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:46,480
right?

171
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,560
It's simple.

172
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:49,440
Just go ahead and do it.

173
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:50,630
Don't hesitate.

174
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:52,560
I can't put Tantan

175
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,920
in any uncertain danger.

176
00:09:54,710 --> 00:09:57,070
Mr. Su said
you could change your destiny.

177
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,480
That's just a possibility.

178
00:09:58,710 --> 00:09:59,920
If I'm not completely sure,

179
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:00,680
I can't...

180
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:02,070
I can't let Tantan take the risk.

181
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,750
Yeah. Fair enough.

182
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:07,070
Too bad.

183
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:10,480
Your beloved is running off with Qiu.

184
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,040
Not him!

185
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,710
Anyone but him.

186
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:14,950
Not anyone!

187
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,830
I'm so scared.

188
00:10:28,710 --> 00:10:29,510
Come here.

189
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,560
Is he still angry?

190
00:10:31,710 --> 00:10:32,240
He's angry.

191
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:33,240
He's very angry.

192
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:36,070
He's horrible when he's angry.
I'm scared.

193
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:39,150
Why does his anger scare you so much?

194
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:40,560
Is it because...

195
00:10:41,070 --> 00:10:42,150
I do like him.

196
00:10:42,950 --> 00:10:44,440
The Marriage Tripod may hear you.

197
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:46,150
It'll get angry.

198
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:47,920
What are you doing?

199
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,480
How could a magic instrument get angry?

200
00:10:51,830 --> 00:10:53,680
I'm going to ask Su Zhinan

201
00:10:53,680 --> 00:10:54,800
how he interpreted my divination stick.

202
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,750
Why isn't my destined love

203
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:57,750
the one I love?

204
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,880
No, I'm going now.

205
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,270
Tantan, wait for me.

206
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,360
Tantan.

207
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,880
Tantan, what's wrong?

208
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:11,630
Mr. Su,

209
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,360
I want a clear explanation now.

210
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,040
Why is it
that my destined love is Qiu Yuebai,

211
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,630
but I like someone else?

212
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:20,560
Your destined love is Mu Bai Zhenren.

213
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:24,390
Your divination is
autumn dew turns into frost since tonight;

214
00:11:24,710 --> 00:11:25,710
the moon viewed at home is more bright.

215
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:26,680
Yeah.

216
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:28,510
Autumn refers to Qiu, moon refers to Yue
and frost refers to Bai.

217
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,680
Isn't it Qiu Yuebai?

218
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,920
The point of the divination is Bai.

219
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,070
I know.

220
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:35,000
Qiu Yuebai. Bai!

221
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:38,880
Zhao Tantan,
your destined love is Mu Bai.

222
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,360
Mu Bai?

223
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:50,440
OK. I see.

224
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:51,040
Tantan.

225
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:51,950
Tantan.

226
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:53,360
Tantan.

227
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,680
It's OK.

228
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,150
They don't know you were mistaken.

229
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,270
Only the three of us know.

230
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,710
I swear I won't tell anyone.

231
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,120
Tantan.

232
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:03,000
We'll definitely keep your secret.

233
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:08,120
Am I the kind of person

234
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,390
who would be bothered by such a thing?

235
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:11,880
My No. 800 rule:

236
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:13,190
as long as I'm not embarrassed,

237
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:14,440
embarrassment can't catch up with me.

238
00:12:15,590 --> 00:12:17,120
What bothers me is...

239
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:18,120
What?

240
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:22,190
Do you think Cui Chen likes me or not?

241
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:24,120
Who knows?

242
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:27,270
I think he does.

243
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:28,830
Why?

244
00:12:29,190 --> 00:12:29,800
Just

245
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:31,630
a hunch.

246
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,320
He looks at you differently.

247
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,880
But I get the feeling

248
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:39,270
that he doesn't care about

249
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,320
the whole destined love thing.

250
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,150
He didn't even ask.

251
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:43,830
I don't know what's on his mind.

252
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,360
I have an idea.

253
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:53,710
What idea?

254
00:12:53,710 --> 00:12:54,830
Yeah, what's your idea?

255
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:58,120
Greatness in simplicity.
Take the initiative.

256
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,510
Tantan, you've changed.

257
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,320
Since you got off the mountain,

258
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,750
I don't understand a word you've said.

259
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,830
Silly you.

260
00:13:08,390 --> 00:13:09,880
What I'm saying is,

261
00:13:10,190 --> 00:13:11,800
don't stay in your room and guess.

262
00:13:12,190 --> 00:13:13,360
Go to see Huai Meng,

263
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:14,920
grab him by the ear and ask him,

264
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,150
"What's on your mind?

265
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:17,360
Do you like me or not?"

266
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:18,590
Is it that simple?

267
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,070
You should do that too.

268
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,710
OK, I'll go now.

269
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,920
What are you doing here?

270
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,510
Manqian, Miss Zhao,

271
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:31,950
Master wants to see you.

272
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:36,710
Mr. Su.

273
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:38,440
This is...

274
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:39,800
Lu Yi.

275
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:41,630
Lu Yi?

276
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:44,360
Is Lu Yi dead?

277
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:46,070
His body was found on the road

278
00:13:46,070 --> 00:13:46,880
from Yunzhou City to Yunlai Town.

279
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,190
What about Hu Meng?

280
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:50,510
We only found Lu Yi.

281
00:13:50,830 --> 00:13:52,120
We didn't find any traces of Hu Meng.

282
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:55,240
Oh, we also found this,

283
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,510
the brocade box
used to keep the lotus seed.

284
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,120
It does smell of the lotus seed.

285
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:06,440
Cui Chen, does Hu Meng
have anything to do with Lu Yi's death?

