00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:35,240
I stretched my wound again.

574
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:35,760
Well...

575
00:31:36,270 --> 00:31:37,910
Huai Meng, come and take a look.

576
00:31:38,080 --> 00:31:38,760
OK.

577
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:40,880
Be careful.

578
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:41,720
Let me take a look.

579
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:44,190
Mr. Qiu, give me your hand.

580
00:31:44,270 --> 00:31:44,960
I'll check your pulse.

581
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:45,880
No.

582
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:47,640
I'm fine.

583
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:49,880
Qiu, how did you get hurt?

584
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:53,670
I wanted to help Tantan.

585
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:55,910
But I'm not good at martial arts.

586
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,640
Unbelievable.

587
00:31:58,790 --> 00:31:59,270
Here.

588
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:01,480
This is my toad coat.

589
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:03,360
It's invulnerable
to weapons, water, and fire.

590
00:32:04,910 --> 00:32:05,910
Why didn't you

591
00:32:05,910 --> 00:32:07,390
ask for my help earlier?

592
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:08,670
Uncle,

593
00:32:08,670 --> 00:32:10,270
we all passed out earlier.

594
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:12,550
We were willing but unable to help.

595
00:32:12,790 --> 00:32:13,310
Yeah.

596
00:32:13,310 --> 00:32:14,240
When did that happen?

597
00:32:14,550 --> 00:32:15,360
- Let's go.
- Well,

598
00:32:15,360 --> 00:32:16,390
- just tell me.
- You know what,

599
00:32:16,390 --> 00:32:17,080
you're showing signs

600
00:32:17,080 --> 00:32:18,480
of senile amnesia.

601
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:20,000
How could you forget it again?

602
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,670
How did we pass out?

603
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:23,030
Tantan.

604
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:25,960
I want to tell you something.

605
00:32:29,030 --> 00:32:30,840
Xueyi, would you give us a minute?

606
00:32:32,430 --> 00:32:33,150
OK, then.

607
00:32:36,190 --> 00:32:37,430
Xueyi, come here.

608
00:32:37,430 --> 00:32:38,030
Xueyi,

609
00:32:39,310 --> 00:32:40,270
what are they talking about?

610
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:43,190
He said he had something to tell Tantan.

611
00:32:43,190 --> 00:32:45,190
He wouldn't let me listen.
He's secretive.

612
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:51,840
Qiu, what do you want to tell me?

613
00:32:52,430 --> 00:32:53,670
I really like you.

614
00:32:54,430 --> 00:32:55,600
I like you too.

615
00:32:55,840 --> 00:32:57,760
Next time, it's my turn to save you.

616
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:58,790
I don't just like you.

617
00:32:59,030 --> 00:33:00,270
I fall for you.

618
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:08,510
Look.

619
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:10,000
They are walking so fast.

620
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,030
We should catch up with them.

621
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:11,600
Gotta go.

622
00:33:11,670 --> 00:33:12,120
Tantan.

623
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:12,960
Xueyi!

624
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:14,670
Xueyi, wait for me!

625
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:22,360
Mr. Cui, why are you stopping me?

626
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:24,550
You didn't take my words seriously,
did you?

627
00:33:25,030 --> 00:33:26,550
You're just her senior.

628
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:28,270
Do you also like her?

629
00:33:29,430 --> 00:33:30,840
I'll tell you again.

630
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:33,150
Anyone who plays tricks behind my back,

631
00:33:33,390 --> 00:33:34,720
I won't let them off easily.

632
00:33:43,190 --> 00:33:45,080
The mountain moon doesn't know
my worries.

633
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:47,790
By the clear water,
flowers fall off silently.

634
00:33:48,190 --> 00:33:48,910
Meaning?

635
00:33:49,670 --> 00:33:52,510
It means you and your beloved

636
00:33:52,670 --> 00:33:54,000
don't seem to be decreed by destiny.

637
00:33:54,670 --> 00:33:58,150
It indicates unrequited love.

638
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:05,270
(I never believe in destiny.)

639
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:08,030
(I only believe in myself.)

640
00:34:25,680 --> 00:34:32,920
[Zhu Village]

641
00:34:47,510 --> 00:34:48,200
Excuse me.

642
00:34:49,680 --> 00:34:51,120
Could you tell me where Zhu Yan lives?

643
00:34:55,230 --> 00:34:56,600
I only asked her a question.

644
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:57,880
Why did she run away?

645
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,400
She must know Zhu Yan,

646
00:34:59,710 --> 00:35:00,950
or she wouldn't be so terrified.

647
00:35:01,470 --> 00:35:02,470
Judging by her response,

648
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:05,030
Zhu Yan must be around here.

